{
  "stem": "21919.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They needed to talk to, after sitting, the two of them, in a small place a whole day long, they would once in a while walk there at night, and- and just have somebody to talk to.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was going on for a long time, till spring came, and most of the straw was gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she was scared, so she told them to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was very sorry to see them go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were my light in a dark tunnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was hoping that one day, when-- when the war is finished and I can tell them who I am, because I- I - I was positive that they didn't suspect anything.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because one day, when it was, they told me, Passover, which I didn't know, and I shouldn't bring them any bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I offered to bring them potatoes that I was boiling in a huge boiler for for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I made sure that I got some oil for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I brought that for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were so moved that one of them said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They-- they were terribly moved that I did extra things for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they kept promising me that after the war, they're going to give me bedding, if I get married.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they have clothes from their wives that they're going to give me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And after the war, they're going to really look after me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was thinking that wait and find out who I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This is the only thing that I was looking forward to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But when spring came, and they had to go away, I didn't hear them being killed, but I didn't know where they went.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
